{"type":"answer","id":25736,"parentType":"question","parentId":4959,"uid":3344,"contents":"因为中共高层家人在邪恶的西方新闻实在太多了，无法一一列出。 既然你觉得的台湾的媒体没有说服力，那我们就随便选两个在国际上比较有分量的报纸，纽约时报和华盛顿邮报来参考一下。<br>\n<br>\n有关于中共领导群家人在巴拿马档案海外存款的报告：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/untrusted fake 2049bbs（钓鱼网站）sultPosition=3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">纽约时报四月六号二零一六年</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n有关于习近平家人因为反腐运动在海外减少资产的报道：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/18/world/asia/chinas-president-xi-jinping-investments.html?searchResultPosition=15\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">纽约时报六月十七号二零一四年</a><br>\n<br>\n有关于中共领导们家人在海外置产移民的报道：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/in-china-relatives-of-party-officials-build-lucrative-businesses-on-family-contacts/2012/04/23/gIQAE56KdT_story.html?noredirect=on&amp;utm_term=.f4854e426999\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">华盛顿邮报四月二十三号二零一二年</a><br>\n<br>\n有关于中共领导群家人把子女送到海外，尤其是美国的报道：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/chinese-communist-leaders-denounce-us-values-but-send-children-to-us-colleges/2012/05/18/gIQAiEidZU_story.html?utm_term=.c8531f45bc85\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">华盛顿邮报五月十九，二零一二年</a>","date":"2019-06-19","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}